(1, 'Blueair Purifiers', 'Air Cleaner Professionals Beijing - Blueair Purifiers', 'Breathe Clean and healthy air in Beijing with Blueair Purifiers from Air Cleaner Professionals. Site Evaluation and indoor air quality testing available', 'Air Cleaner Professionals - Blueair Purifiers', '<p>\r\n	With Blueair air purifier systems, you can surround yourself with air that is virtually free from impurities &mdash; wherever you are.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Our broad range of world-class room air purifiers meet virtually every requirement for people living with asthma, allergies, pets and smokers as well as special considerations given to children and seniors.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	What&rsquo;s clear is that Blueair systems significantly improve the indoor air quality in your home &ndash; virtually eliminating dust, pollen, mold, smoke and other airborne pollutants. Breathe easy!</p>\r\n', '14103Blueair_Purifiers.jpg', 1),
(2, 'Filters', 'Air Cleaner Professionals Beijing - Buy Blueair Filters', 'Blueair Smokestop filters are the ideal choice for allergy and asthma sufferers as well as other health conscious people that need high efficiency particle removal', 'Air Cleaner Professionals - Blueair Filters', '<p>\r\n	Replacing the Blueair filters according to manufacturer recommendations is critical to ensuring that your Blueair air purifying system keeps performing as it should. It is recommended that filters be replaced every 6 months for optimal use.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Blueair Smokestop Filters are the ideal choice for allergy and asthma sufferers as well as other health-conscious individuals that need high-efficiency particle removal. The Go Smokestop filter is a progressive carbon filter technology generally provides higher filtration performance than other air purifiers, trapping up to six times more dirt. The fibers effectively capture 99.97% of airborne particles such as allergens, pollen, mold spores, dust, pet dander, gas, odor and other heavy pollutants. Perfect for Beijing.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="bottom_box">\r\n	<img alt="" height="200" src="images/689122000077_sm.jpg" width="200" /><br />\r\n	<p>\r\n		BlueAir 500/600 Series SmokeStop Filter Kit</p>\r\n	<div class="price">\r\n		RMB 798</div>\r\n	<div class="price">\r\n		<span style="color: #ff0000">In Stock&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="bottom_box">\r\n	<img alt="" height="200" src="images/689122000145_sm.jpg" width="200" /><br />\r\n	<p>\r\n		BlueAir 400 Series SmokeStop Filter</p>\r\n	<div class="price">\r\n		RMB 598</div>\r\n	<div class="price">\r\n		<span style="color: #ff0000">In Stock&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="bottom_box" style="margin-right: 0px">\r\n	<img alt="" height="200" src="images/689122001302_sm.jpg" width="200" /><br />\r\n	<p>\r\n		BlueAir 200 Series SmokeStop Filter</p>\r\n	<div class="price">\r\n		RMB 398</div>\r\n	<div class="price">\r\n		<span style="color: #ff0000">In Stock</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '9988filter.jpg', 1),
(3, 'Service Packages', 'Air Cleaner Professionals Beijing- Service Packages', 'Air Cleaner Professionals Beijing', 'Air Cleaner Professionals - Service Packages', '<h1>\r\n	Site Evaluation Package</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n	If you are not sure which Blueair Purifier suits your needs, you can call us to do a site evaluation. Basically, we come over to your home or place of business and consult you on which combination of Blueair Purifiers will meet your needs.We will also do an indoor air quality test (PM2.5) to show you how healthy the air is at your premisis.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>Evaluation of a site consists of the following</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="margin-left: 30px">\r\n	1. Number of rooms<br />\r\n	2. Size of rooms<br />\r\n	3. Room Layout<br />\r\n	4. Electrical socket positions<br />\r\n	5. Indoor air quality test of each room<br />\r\n	6. Comparison to the outdoor air quality</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Cost : <strong>RMB250</strong>. Free if&nbsp;a purifier is purchased. Client has one week to purchase from date of evaluation to qualify for free evaluation.</p>\r\n<h1 style="margin-top: 30px">\r\n	Site Evaluation and Demonstration Package</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n	In addition to the above site evaluation package we can also bring a demo purifier and show you how they work.. First we do an air quality test. Then we connect our Blueair Purifier in one room. 10 mins later, we do another air quailty test and show you the results. The improvement in air quality will amaze you!<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	(Air Quality tests show level of PM2.5 particles as measured by the World Health Organization and US Embassy in Beijing.)<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Cost: <strong>RMB350</strong>. Free if a purifier is purchased. Client has one week to purchase from date of evaluation to qualify for free evaluation</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="condition">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '2470contact_img2.jpg', 1),
(4, 'Faq', 'Air Cleaner Professionals Beijing - Blueair Purifier Faq', 'Start breathing clean and healthy air in Beijing with Blueair Purifiers from Air Cleaner Professionals. Indoor air quality testing and site evaluation available', 'Air Cleaner Professionals - FAQ', '<h2 style="margin-top: 25px">\r\n	General Questions</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	Do I need an air purifier?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	If you live in Beijing, the answer would be absolutely yes. And we&rsquo;re not just saying that because we sell them. Fumes from car exhausts and factories from the surrounding areas can take the air pollution to hazardous levels on many days. (See US Embassy site for pollution levels) Therefore opening windows to let the air in is out of the question. The only way to clean the air indoors is through an air purifier.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	Who can an air purifier help?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	In Beijing, pretty much everyone. However, children, the elderly as well as people with allergies and respiratory issues are helped the most.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	Why should I buy an air purifier from you?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Air Purifiers are specialised products. It is best to purchase them from a professional who can advise you on how to use them most effectively.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Where can I check the air pollution level?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	There are a few apps where you can check the pollution levels in Beijing. Go to the app store of your device and search for &ldquo;Beijing air quality&rdquo;. The US Embassy also provides a twitter feed every hour on air pollution levels.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	What does HEPA stand for and why is it important?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	High Efficiency Particulate Air. This is important because the air contains a lot of small particles which can be absorbed into the lungs. Our Air purifiers can filter out 99.8% of these particles thereby making the air very healthy for you to breathe.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Do you offer consultancy in English?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Absolutely.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Questions about Purchase and delivery</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	How can I purchase a Blueair Purifier from you?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	You can either send us an email at <span style="color: #0099ff">info@aircleanerpros.com</span>&nbsp;or you may call us at <span style="color: #0066ff">13661143811</span>. We cannot do online purchases at this time.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Can you help me select a model?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Yes we can! You can ask for a <a href="http://www.aircleanerpros.com/service_packages.php">Site Evaluation</a>&nbsp;and we&rsquo;ll come over and consult you on which models will suit your needs and how many you may need for your home or office.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	How long does a site evaluation take?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Usually a site evaluation takes about 30 mins or so.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Do you charge for site evaluation?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Unfortunately because Beijing is so large and it takes a long time to go from place to place, we do charge a nominal fee of RMB 250 to do this. However, if you buy an air purifier from us, this fee will be waived.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	When can you deliver?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Typically we take 2-3 days to deliver. However, depending on the model and the demand at the time (due to the pollution level), it may take longer.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Do you deliver outside Beijing?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	At this time, we do not deliver outside Beijing.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Do you accept credit cards or bank cards?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	We are working on it, but at this time, we only accept cash.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Do you have a return policy?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Within the first 7 days, you may exchange the air purifier for another one if there is any defect. Please also make sure you do not throw away the box within this time. We do not give refunds.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Questions about Products</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	Are the air purifiers loud?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	No. Blueair Purifiers run on HEPA silent technology. They are some of the quietest purifiers on the market running between 30 and 50 decibels. So you can sleep and work without knowing they&rsquo;re even there.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Do they take up a lot of electricity?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Blueair Purifiers have the energy star certificate and cost as much to run as a light bulb.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	How do I know if the air purifiers work?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	We can do a <a href="http://www.aircleanerpros.com/service_packages.php" style="text-decoration: underline">demonstration</a> in your home or office and prove it to you</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	How often should I run my air purifier?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	You should run your air purifier 24 hours a day.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	On which setting should I run the purifier?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	It really depends on the pollution level that day. For Moderate pollution, you may run on low speed, for unhealthy pollution, on medium speed and for hazardous pollution on high speed.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	How many air purifiers do I need?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	That really depends on the size of your home or office. We have models for many different sized rooms. You can compare models <a href="http://www.aircleanerpros.com/compare.php">here</a>. Or you can call us for a <a href="http://www.aircleanerpros.com/service_packages.php">Site Evaluation</a>.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	How long is the warrantee on the air purifiers?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	We stand by the quality of our products. The warrantee lasts for 5 years from the date of purchase for all models except the 203, which is 3 years<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	My air purifier doesn&rsquo;t work. What should I do?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Give us a call and we&rsquo;ll send someone to collect it for repair</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Questions about filters</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	How do I know when to change the filter?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	We will remind you by sending you a text message. Also, your purifier has a timer to change the filter and it will start to flash when the time comes. We will then deliver the filter to you on request.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Is it complicated to change the filter?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	No, it&rsquo;s very easy and takes just 30 seconds.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	<br />\r\n	How often should I change the filters?</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	For optimal use, you should change the filters every 6 months.</p>\r\n', '24551faq_img.jpg', 1),
