erif">Email contact</span></span></u></p>\r\n<p class="condition">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;">For&nbsp;information : </span><a href="mailto:info@aircleanerpros.com" style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;">info@aircleanerpros.com</a></span></p>\r\n<p class="condition">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif">For support : <a href="mailto:support@aircleanerpros.com">support@aircleanerpros.com</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="condition">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="condition">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '32662contact_img1.jpg', 1),
