(1, 1, 'Model 203', '203', 3800, 3590, 0, '7962product1.jpg', '<p>\r\n	A perfect bedroom companion, the Blueair 203 packs a complete, high-performance air purifier into a beautifully compact design that&rsquo;s incredibly quiet.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	But you don&rsquo;t have to leave the Blueair 203 in the bedroom. It&rsquo;s also great in small areas and workspaces to get rid of pesky airborne allergens, such as pollen, dust, smoke, mold spores, pet dander and other impurities.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	All that remains? Impeccably clean air.</p>\r\n', 'The strong, silent type', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 155, '3', 'Back', 'Top', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Adam_VLR.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	&bull; Ideal for small rooms (240 ft2 or 22 m2)<br />\r\n	&bull; 99.97% filtration efficiency<br />\r\n	&bull; Energy Star&reg; qualified<br />\r\n	&bull; Includes filter replacement indicator</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Blue_diode_closeup.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	The union of visually pleasing form and effective function is a hallmark of Swedish design, and Blueair is no exception. The Blueair 203 is designed for maximum performance in small rooms.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/203Silver.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s patented HEPASilent&trade; technology combines the best features of electrostatic and mechanical filter technology to enable the delivery of more clean air at a faster rate with less noise. Phenomenally low power usage minimizes energy consumption. Plus Blueair air purifiers actually reduce the levels of ozone in indoor air.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/200.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Air is drawn into the unit via an ultra-quiet fan. Airborne particles pass through an ion chamber and are charged to ensure that they adhere effortlessly to Blueair&rsquo;s progressive three-stage filter. Cleaned air that is free of impurities is recirculated into the room.</div>\r\n', 1),
(2, 1, 'Model 270E', '270E', 5000, 4590, 1, '31670270e-remote.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="images/270e-remote.jpg" style="border-bottom: #e5e6eb 1px solid; border-left: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; background: #ffffff; float: left; border-top: #e5e6eb 1px solid; margin-right: 15px; border-right: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-top: 6px" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	For the gadget-happy, the popular Blueair 270E offers the same reliable air purification performance as the incredibly quiet Blueair 203 model, but it comes with a handy remote control unit and digital display.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The easy-to-use remote control and digital display system give you instant feedback of particle detection, air purifier speed and timer operation. So you don&rsquo;t have to leave your comfortable spot at your desk, on the sofa or in bed to change the speed setting. Just point and click.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Electronic particle and gas sensors confirm that the unit is effectively removing allergens, such as pollen, dust, smoke, mold spores and pet dander, from the air. And you can see when it&#39;s time to change the filters on the electronic display.</p>\r\n', 'Electronic control', 20, 1, 1, 0, 1, 155, '3+Auto', 'Back', 'Top', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Adam_VLR.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	&bull; Ideal for small rooms (240 ft2 or 22 m2)<br />\r\n	&bull; 99.97% filtration efficiency<br />\r\n	&bull; Energy Star&reg; qualified</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Blue_diode_closeup.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	The union of visually pleasing form and effective function is a hallmark of Swedish design, and Blueair is no exception. The Blueair 270E is designed for maximum performance in small rooms.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/203Silver.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s patented HEPASilent&trade; technology combines the best features of electrostatic and mechanical filter technology to enable the delivery of more clean air at a faster rate with less noise. Phenomenally low power usage minimizes energy consumption. Plus Blueair air purifiers actually reduce the levels of ozone in indoor air.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/200.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Air is drawn into the unit via an ultra-quiet fan. Airborne particles pass through an ion chamber and are charged to ensure that they adhere effortlessly to Blueair&rsquo;s progressive three-stage filter. Cleaned air that is free of impurities is recirculated into the room.</div>\r\n', 1),
(3, 2, 'Model 403', '403', 6000, 5650, 0, '21945403.jpg', '<p>\r\n	Experience the crisp feeling of cleaner air brought to you by the model that made Blueair a world leader in air purifier design and technology.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Although this unit is designed to clear the air in mid-sized rooms, there&rsquo;s nothing middle of the road about the Blueair 403. Ingeniously designed and brilliantly engineered, the Blueair 403 is based on the absolute original Blueair air purifier first tested at the prestigious Karolinska University Hospital in Stockholm over a decade ago.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The Blueair 403 continues to deliver outstanding performance that has withstood the test of time. Using patented HEPASilent&trade; technology, it captures 99.97% of the tiniest 0.1 micron particles on level one, including allergy-provoking pollen grains, dust mites, mold spores and pet dander particles.</p>\r\n', 'The tried-and-true original', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 240, '4', 'Side', 'Side', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Adam_VLR.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	&bull; Ideal for mid-sized rooms (365 ft2 or 34 m2)<br />\r\n	&bull; 99.97% filtration efficiency<br />\r\n	&bull; Energy Star&reg; qualified<br />\r\n	&bull; Includes filter replacement indicator</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Blue_diode_closeup.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	The union of visually pleasing form and effective function is a hallmark of Swedish design, and Blueair is no exception. The Blueair 403 is designed for maximum performance in mid-sized rooms. Available in white/dark grey, it suits your distinct style of living.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/203Silver.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s patented HEPASilent&trade; technology combines the best features of electrostatic and mechanical filter technology to enable the delivery of more clean air at a faster rate with less noise. Phenomenally low power usage minimizes energy consumption. Plus Blueair air purifiers actually reduce the levels of ozone in indoor air.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/403-series.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Air is drawn into the unit via an ultra-quiet fan. Airborne particles pass through an ion chamber and are charged to ensure that they adhere effortlessly to Blueair&rsquo;s progressive three-stage filter. Cleaned air that is free of impurities is recirculated into the room.</div>\r\n', 1),
(4, 2, 'Model 450E', '450E', 6800, 6460, 1, '29728450.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="images/digital_display.gif" style="border-bottom: #e5e6eb 1px solid; border-left: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; background: #ffffff; float: left; border-top: #e5e6eb 1px solid; margin-right: 15px; border-right: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-top: 6px" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Continuously monitor and purify your indoor air with the Blueair 450E air purifier. Simply click on the unit&#39;s handy remote control from distances of up to 6 meters or 20 feet away to change the operating speed or set the on/off timer. Or set your unit on auto mode and let it regulate itself.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The easy-to-use remote control and digital display system give you instant feedback of particle detection, air purifier speed and timer operation. So you don&rsquo;t have to leave your comfortable spot at your desk, on the sofa or in bed to change the speed setting. Just point and click. Plus you can see when it&#39;s time to change the filters on the electronic display.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="images/450-series.jpg" style="border-bottom: #e5e6eb 1px solid; border-left: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; background: #ffffff; float: left; border-top: #e5e6eb 1px solid; margin-right: 15px; border-right: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-top: 6px" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Electronic particle and gas sensors confirm that the unit is effectively removing allergens, such as pollen, dust, mold spores and pet dander from the air.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Patented HEPASilent&trade; filter technology removes 99.97% of all airborne contaminants, such as smoke, dust, pollen and volatile organic compounds, that are 0.1 micron or larger in size.</p>\r\n', 'The tried-and-true original goes digital', 34, 1, 1, 0, 1, 240, '4+Auto', 'Side', 'Side', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Adam_VLR.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	&bull; Ideal for mid-sized rooms (365 ft2 or 34 m2)<br />\r\n	&bull; 99.97% filtration efficiency<br />\r\n	&bull; Energy Star&reg; qualified</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Blue_diode_closeup.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	The union of visually pleasing form and effective function is a hallmark of Swedish design, and Blueair is no exception. The Blueair 450E is designed for maximum performance in mid-sized rooms.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/203Silver.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s patented HEPASilent&trade; technology combines the best features of electrostatic and mechanical filter technology to enable the delivery of more clean air at a faster rate with less noise. Phenomenally low power usage minimizes energy consumption. Plus Blueair air purifiers actually reduce the levels of ozone in indoor air.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/200.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Air is drawn into the unit via an ultra-quiet fan. Airborne particles pass through an ion chamber and are charged to ensure that they adhere effortlessly to Blueair&rsquo;s progressive three-stage filter. Cleaned air that is free of impurities is recirculated into the room.</div>\r\n', 1),
(5, 3, 'Model 503', '503', 7400, 6860, 0, '25284403.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<strong>Living spaciously?</strong> The Blueair 503 is an excellent choice for people living with allergies, asthma, or other respiratory conditions, or for anyone who wants cleaner, more breathable air.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Designed for large rooms up to 54 m2 (580 ft2), the Blueair 503 effectively purifies indoor air. This powerful air purifier offers quiet operation by gently diffusing air through an area six times greater than the average air clenaer, thanks to its SurroundAir&trade; system.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	This provides an exceptional air exchange rate and better indoor air quality. Plus you can easily move the Blueair 503 around your living space thanks to convenient caster wheels.</p>\r\n', 'Stylish simplicity', 54, 0, 0, 1, 0, 375, '4', 'Bottom and Sides', 'Top and Sides', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Adam_VLR.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	&bull; Ideal for large rooms (580ft2 or 54m2)<br />\r\n	&bull; 99.97% filtration efficiency<br />\r\n	&bull; Energy Star&reg; qualified<br />\r\n	&bull; Includes filter replacement indicator</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Blue_diode_closeup.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	The union of visually pleasing form and effective function is a hallmark of Swedish design, and Blueair is no exception. The Blueair 503 us designed for max&iacute;mum performance in large rooms. Available in white/darkgrey, it suits your distinct style of living. Convenient caster wheels lets you easily move your Blueair from room to room.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/203Silver.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s patented HEPASilent&trade; technology combines the best features of electrostatic and mechanical filter technology to enable the delivery of more clean air at a faster rate with less noise. Phenomenally low power usage minimizes energy consumption. Plus Blueair air purifiers actually reduce the levels of ozone in the indoor air.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/503-series.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s SurroundAir&trade; system achieves peak performance by drawing in dirty air from the sides and bottom and releasing clean, filtered air from the sides and top. Cleaned air that is free of impurities is recirculated into the room.</div>\r\n', 1),
(6, 3, 'Model 550E', '550E', 8000, 7550, 0, '4893450.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="images/450-series.jpg" style="border-bottom: #e5e6eb 1px solid; border-left: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; background: #ffffff; float: left; border-top: #e5e6eb 1px solid; margin-right: 15px; border-right: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-top: 6px" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	For the gadget-happy, the popular Blueair 550E offers the same reliable air purification performance as the incredibly quiet Blueair 503 model, but it comes with a handy remote control unit and digital display.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The easy-to-use remote control and digital display system gives you instant feedback of particle detection, air purifier speed and timer operation. So you don&rsquo;t have to leave your comfortable spot at your desk, on the sofa or in bed to change the speed setting. Just point and click.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="images/digital_display.gif" style="border-bottom: #e5e6eb 1px solid; border-left: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; background: #ffffff; float: left; border-top: #e5e6eb 1px solid; margin-right: 15px; border-right: #e5e6eb 1px solid; padding-top: 6px" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Electronic particle and gas sensors confirm that the unit is effectively removing allergens, such as pollen, dust, smoke, mold spores and pet dander, from the air. And you can see when it&#39;s time to change the filters on the electronic display.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Stylish simplicity with electronic control', 54, 1, 1, 1, 1, 373, '4+Auto', 'Bottom and Sides', 'Top and Sides', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Adam_VLR.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	&bull; Ideal for large rooms (580 ft2 or 54 m2)<br />\r\n	&bull; 99.97% filtration efficiency<br />\r\n	&bull; Energy Star&reg; qualified</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Blue_diode_closeup.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	The union of visually pleasing form and effective function is a hallmark of Swedish design, and Blueair is no exception. The Blueair 550E is designed for maximum performance in large rooms. Available in white or dark grey, it suits your distinct style of living. Convenient caster wheels let you easily move your Blueair from room to room.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/203Silver.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s patented HEPASilent&trade; technology combines the best features of electrostatic and mechanical filter technology to enable the delivery of more clean air at a faster rate with less noise. Phenomenally low power usage minimizes energy consumption. Plus Blueair air purifiers actually reduce the levels of ozone in indoor air.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/503-series.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&rsquo;s SurroundAir&trade; system achieves peak performance by drawing in dirty air from the sides and bottom and releasing clean, filtered air from the sides and top. When operating on the lowest setting, the air purifiers do not create any noticeable draft. On the highest setting, the units provide maximum coverage with minimum draft. Cleaned air that is free of impurities is recirculated into the room.</div>\r\n', 1),
(7, 4, 'Model 603', '603', 13000, 11980, 0, '12723600.jpg', '<p>\r\n	For amazingly powerful air purification, there&rsquo;s the Blueair 603. From its powerful fan engine to its SurroundAir filtration technology, this Blueair is the most powerful Blueair ever.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Best for very large rooms up to 65 m2 (698 ft2), this powerhouse delivers dramatic improvements in efficiency, earning the Blueair 603 even better Clean Air Delivery Rates than the Blueair 503.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Plus you can easily move the Blueair 603 around your living space thanks to convenient caster wheels on the bottom of the unit.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Powerful purification', 65, 0, 0, 1, 0, 450, '4', 'Bottom and Sides', 'Top and Sides', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Adam_VLR.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	&bull; Ideal for very large rooms (698 ft2 or 65 m2)<br />\r\n	&bull; 99.97% filtration efficiency<br />\r\n	&bull; Energy Star&reg; qualified<br />\r\n	&bull; Includes filter replacement indicator</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/203Silver.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	The union of visually pleasing form and effective function is a hallmark of Swedish design, and Blueair is no exception. The Blueair 603 is designed for maximum performance in large rooms. Available in white or dark grey, it suits your distinct style of living. Convenient caster wheels let you easily move your Blueair from room to room.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/Blue_diode_closeup.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&#39;s patented HEPASilent&trade; technology combines the best features of electrostatic and mechanical filter technology to enable the delivery of more clean air at a faster rate with less noise. Phenomenally low power usage minimizes energy consumption. Plus Blueair air purifiers actually reduce the levels of ozone in indoor air.</div>\r\n', '<div class="Lpart">\r\n	<img alt="" class="img" src="images/600-series.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="Rpart">\r\n	Blueair&rsquo;s SurroundAir&trade; system achieves peak performance by drawing in dirty air from the sides and bottom and releasing clean, filtered air from the sides and top. When operating on the lowest setting, the air purifiers do not create any noticeable draft. On the highest setting, the units provide maximum coverage with minimum draft. Cleaned air that is free of impurities is recirculated into the room.</div>\r\n', 1);

